About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The residents of the housing society, help each other find solutions when they face common, real-life challenges and get involved in sticky situations.

snippet.description:
Armaan Music Presenting You The New Odia Romantic Full Music Video song " Mu Heigali Ajithu Tora " Starring By Rupa & Pintu . This Romantic Hit Track sung By Udit Narayan & Ira Mohanty . This Odia Music Video " Mu Heigali Ajithu Tora " Is Directed By Somio R , Penned By Panchanan Nayak And Music By Your All Time Favorite Japani Bhai .Please Enjoy And Share Rupa & Pintu New Odia Album Song " Mu Heigali Ajithu Tora " . We Hope This Romantic Song Must Be a Big Hit .

Audio Credits

Song - Mu Heigali Ajithu Tora
Lyrics - Panchanan Nayak
Music - Japani Bhai
Singer - Udit Narayan & Ira Mohanty
Keyboard Programming - Jaga Jd
Rythm - Anil Das
Recording Studio - RT Studio ( Mumbai ) & Milan Studio
Recordist - Rupak Thakur & Soubhagya Panda
Mixing & Mastering - Milan Das
Special Thanks - Bibek & Ashutosh

Starring - Rupa & Pintu
Direction - Somio R

Choreographer - Nandu Master
Edit - Ranjan Khatei
Di - Srujan Films

Poster - Piyush
Spot - Lalit

Travells - Anil

Special Thanks - Omm

"Mu Heigali Ajithu Tora"
Lyrics:-

Mukhuda:-
**************
M:-
Aji phagunare lagigala ranga
              Sei ranga aji deigala daga

Cross:-
Hrudaya jadi delu tu mate
       De kahile debi mu tate, tope sindura

Tag:-
F:-
Mu heigali heigali heigali heigali
                 Ajithu tora.....(‡≠¶)
M:-
Tu heigalu heigalu heigalu heigalu 
                 Ajithu mora.....(‡≠¶)



Antara:-01
***************
M:-
Piladine gote kahani te sunithili
       Aakasha deshare pari tie thae boli
           Tu sei pari, aji janigali

F:-
Kebe dine gote kabita te padhithili
         Sagara majhire raja tie rahe boli
               Tu sei raja, aji chinhi gali

Cross:-
M:-
Chhatire tate rakhibaa pain
        Sata sagara asichi dein, debi sindura

Tag:-
F:-
Mu heigali heigali heigali heigali
                 Ajithu tora.....(01)
M:-
Tu heigalu heigalu heigalu heigalu
                 Ajithu mora.....(01)

Antara:-02
**************
F:-
Dinaku dina mu saja hue beshi kain 
   Aina kahuchi to pari sundari nahi
           Mu bodhe to bata, rahichi chahi

M:-
Aakasha taa aji pruthibi ku chhuindela
      Nijathu nijara kehi jane miligala
            To bata mo bata, gotie hela

Cross:-
F:-
 Manaku gote mana milila
      Aau ja khali baki rahila, tope sindura

Tag:-
M:-
Mu heigali heigali heigali heigali
                 Ajithu tora.....(02)
F:-
Tu heigalu heigalu heigalu heigalu 
                 Ajithu mora.....(02)

Jasmin Jaffer, who has faced a lot of challenges in her life and is a popular influencer on social media, tells her life story on Josh Talks.

Jasmine Jaffer is a remarkable force of influence who has overcome many challenges and hardships in her life and become an inspiration to many people. Jasmine's early life was filled with many struggles and setbacks. She was born and brought up in a family with limited financial resources and her parents often struggled to make ends meet.

Jasmine Jaffer is incredibly influential and an inspiration to everyone struggling in life. Her story is a testament to the power of positivity, perseverance and determination, and it shows that no matter what challenges we face, we can overcome them and achieve our dreams if we commit to our goals.

Josh Talks passionately believes that a well-told story has the power to reshape attitudes, lives, and ultimately, the world. We are on a mission to find and showcase the best motivational stories from across India through documented videos and live events held all over the country. Josh Talks Malayalam caters to the Malayalam-speaking audience worldwide. It aims to inspire and motivate Malayalees by showcasing Malayalam motivation through the experiences of fellow Malayalis. Josh talks Malayalam and brings to you the best Malayalam motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women‚Äôs rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. Jasmine Jaffer is a remarkable force of influence who has overcome many challenges and hardships in her life and become an inspiration to many people. Jasmine's early life was filled with many struggles and setbacks. She was born and brought up in a family with limited financial resources and her parents often struggled to make ends meet.

Jasmine Jaffer is incredibly influential and an inspiration to everyone struggling in life. snippet.title: India Travel Vlog in Tamil | Alandra's Adventure in India - Steffi Ulagam
snippet.description:
In this video, I am sharing some of the highlights from my recent trip to India. This was Alandra's second visit to India and this time, she had a lot of fun visiting the farm, beach, seeing all relatives and shopping. I was in India for 6 weeks and Alandra had a blast. She also had a lot of fun with cats and trying the different fruits there.
#steffiulagam #steffivlogs

Friends, hope you liked this week's vlog. While, I don't think I can do the weekly vlogs in Steffi Ulagam, I will occasionally share some of the events and interesting things in Madras Samayal. Thank you so much for your love and support.

snippet.title: Minecraft Hostage Simulator
snippet.description:
Minecraft Hostage Simulator... this was the most ridiculous challenge we have ever done. It was absurd.

Follow my socials:
‚ûΩ Twitter - @dream
‚ûΩ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
‚ûΩ Snapchat - @dream

BadBoyHalo: @thesaintsofgames 
George: @GeorgeNotFound 
Sapnap: @Sapnap 

This video is a different Minecraft challenge concept that we have never done before!

In this challenge, BadBoyHalo is a hostage and we have to try and take him to the end portal. There are two teams, I am on one, and GeorgeNotFound & Sapnap are the other. BadBoyHalo can try and escape, but he can't break the rope that he's attached to.

It's a race, and it's super intense and we had a lot of laughs. I love doing these challenges.

Not Minecraft, But Water Rises or Minecraft, But Lava Rises, or any other but challenge like that. This is a speed run / speed runner of Minecraft against a killer / assassin

#MinecraftChallenge

snippet.title: Why Rahul Gandhi was disqualified as Lok Sabha MP after conviction? IN NEWS | Drishti IAS
snippet.description:
Today‚Äôs InNews PDF Telegram Link: https://t.me/innewsdrishtiias

Why Rahul Gandhi was disqualified as Lok Sabha MP after conviction? 

Congress leader Rahul Gandhi has been disqualified from the Lok Sabha, a day after he was convicted in a defamation case by a Surat court. A notice issued by the Lok Sabha Secretariat said he stood disqualified from the House from March 23, the day of his conviction. Rahul Gandhi has to now move a higher court and get his conviction stayed. Chief Judicial Magistrate HH Verma convicted Gandhi in a 2019 defamation case, for saying ‚Äòwhy do all thieves have the name Modi‚Äô, and sentenced him to two years in prison. The remarks were made during a rally in Kolar, Karnataka, in the run-up to the 2019 Lok Sabha elections. ‚ÄúWhy do all thieves, be it Nirav Modi, Lalit Modi or Narendra Modi, have Modi in their names,‚Äù Gandhi had said in Hindi.

localized.description:
Today‚Äôs InNews PDF Telegram Link: https://t.me/innewsdrishtiias

Why Rahul Gandhi was disqualified as Lok Sabha MP after conviction? 

Congress leader Rahul Gandhi has been disqualified from the Lok Sabha, a day after he was convicted in a defamation case by a Surat court. A notice issued by the Lok Sabha Secretariat said he stood disqualified from the House from March 23, the day of his conviction. Rahul Gandhi has to now move a higher court and get his conviction stayed. Chief Judicial Magistrate HH Verma convicted Gandhi in a 2019 defamation case, for saying ‚Äòwhy do all thieves have the name Modi‚Äô, and sentenced him to two years in prison. The remarks were made during a rally in Kolar, Karnataka, in the run-up to the 2019 Lok Sabha elections. ‚ÄúWhy do all thieves, be it Nirav Modi, Lalit Modi or Narendra Modi, have Modi in their names,‚Äù Gandhi had said in Hindi.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3728 - 25 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3728: Nayi Scheme
--------------------------------------------------------
Rustom the new area manager of Ramsang company plans to blacklist Gada Electronics for the unprofessional behavior of Jethalal as he was late to the meeting. Rustom tries to run from the Gada electronics, but Jetha chases him as he misunderstood him to be a thief. Later, Rustom meets Jethalal in his shop, where he explains the new scheme to him on account of the 25th year anniversary of the company. Watch the episode 

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3728, 25 Mar 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Link to our blog: https://beerbiceps.com/2023/03/25/unpopular-opinions-of-the-world-celebrated-journalist-palki-sharma-opens-up/

Our guest for this episode is a Celebrated Journalist, Managing Editor, Firstpost and award-winning Indian news anchor Palki Sharma in conversation with Ranveer Allahbadia - A conversation touching a broad spectrum of topics. Underlying the importance of self-acceptance, this podcast will nudge you on the road to introspection.

In this podcast, we spoke about the different media narratives, the representation of journalism, her Interview with Perez Musharraf, China's war with Taiwan, the future of Pakistan & so much more.

India's Top Journalist Palki Sharma on News & Media, its representation & geopolitics. Hope you enjoy this lovely chat. 

(0:00) - Ranveer x Palki Sharma Begins
(4:05) - Media narratives in India
(10:00) - How are Indian journalists represented?
(15:27) - Interview with Perez Musharraf
(21:40) - China's secrets of progress
(30:40) - China's war with Taiwan?
(38:20) - What is the future of Pakistan?
(42:17) - Her commentary on the USA
(50:22) - Why emotion can overpower data?
(53:15) - Thank you for watching

#journalism #palkisharma

Tere Bin Episode 27 Teaser - 23rd March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Tere Bin Episode 27 Teaser - 23rd March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3727 - 24 Mar 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3727: Rickshaw Kahan Hain?
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha gets swooned by Babita's traditional dressing style and offers her a ride. Fortunately, Babita Ji was also attending the function at her friend's place, which happens to be near Jetha's shop, so she accepted the offer. Popatlal objects to Jetha stating that only three people could ride in an auto rickshaw so Taarak suggests that they should take a cab. Jetha is already anxious about his meeting with Ramsong's Area Manager, Mr. Rustom, who happens to be very punctual, but he also cannot miss the chance to commute alongside Babita Ji. Will Jetha be able to attend the meeting or is there a new trouble hovering?¬†

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha gets swooned by Babita's traditional dressing style and offers her a ride. Fortunately, Babita Ji was also attending the function at her friend's place, which happens to be near Jetha's shop, so she accepted the offer. Popatlal objects to Jetha stating that only three people could ride in an auto rickshaw so Taarak suggests that they should take a cab. Jetha is already anxious about his meeting with Ramsong's Area Manager, Mr. Rustom, who happens to be very punctual, but he also cannot miss the chance to commute alongside Babita Ji. Episode 3: Kaashvi's Life In Danger
-------------------------------------------------
Baalveer spends some quality time with his mother, and she thanks him for saving his life and asks him to spend time with her more often. snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 25 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 22nd March 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Yumna Zaidi as Meerab

Bushra Ansari as Salma

snippet.title: BIG ICE CREAM | Biggest Stick ice making | Watermelon ice | Kiwi ice | Milk ice | Fruit ice Making
snippet.description:
In our childhood, we enjoy those moments with tasting stick ice. We call this ice "Kuchi ice". Today in our village, we made the three most giant colorful stick ice with fruits and milk. We made three types of ice cream. The first one is milk. The second is watermelon. The third one is Kiwi.

Childhood memory comes again! Tasty!
